{"tid":827011,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iphone xr一定有得炒，因為六隻色無可能隻隻都齊貨，尤其係黃色同藍色","createTime":"2018-09-18T15:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T08:36:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"88727da23722a2a826f7d4fa7d30c79721f22903","tid":827011,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"有錢人一定係買晒七隻色（包埋iphonex max金色）方便襯衫，黃色藍色最正一定多人搶，依家好似盛傳xr會缺貨，炒上二萬都有可能"},{"pid":"d21ac523ece8de84482d78dac3f718f568effac4","tid":827011,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"想炒新iPhone？呢款機可能值得一博！<br />\n<br />\n【iPhone XR每日僅生產30萬部　十月恐缺貨】<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NSMkIb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NSMkIb&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ca4d9853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2NSMkIb</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外媒報道，來自主要iPhone代工商富士康的消息透露，由於零部件商出現LCD屏幕配件供貨短缺，導致整個組裝也被迫推遲。最新消息指，現時富士康每日只可生產30萬部iPhone XR左右，估計10月26日交貨時，大部分「果粉」未必可以即時取到新機。 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，Apple新發布會當日已傳出iPhone XR的玻璃機背出現供貨短缺情況，致使該款專攻內地市場的廉價版iPhone，不能在9月22日與另外兩大新款iPhone同日接受預訂，而推遲至10月才開始接受預訂及發貨。"},{"pid":"588a0b29c58c168f9a2cad2d327190b51a3fe279","tid":827011,"uid":12628,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:46:01.000Z","msg":"炒車就有得炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8d857fef46ec64058ba2af82e591e3fcff81c1","tid":827011,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"588a0b29c58c168f9a2cad2d327190b51a3fe279","tid":827011,"uid":12628,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:46:01.000Z","msg":"炒車就有得炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T15:57:58.000Z","msg":"唔可能囉"},{"pid":"59b659f0bcd20576c8327ad30c5933d02cd3180d","tid":827011,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T18:1